sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as External Client
    participant Router as OpenShift Router<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.3
    participant Service as {registry-name} Service<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Proxy as kube-rbac-proxy<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Registry as model-registry REST<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
    participant DB as PostgreSQL<br/>5432/TCP TLS (optional)

    Note over Client,DB: Flow 1: External User Access to Model Registry (Secured)

    Client->>Router: POST /api/model_registry/v1alpha3/registered_models<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    Router->>Service: Forward (reencrypt TLS)<br/>8443/TCP
    Service->>Proxy: HTTPS Request<br/>Bearer Token

    Proxy->>K8sAPI: SubjectAccessReview<br/>TLS 1.2+<br/>ServiceAccount token
    K8sAPI-->>Proxy: Authorization Result<br/>(allow/deny)

    alt Authorized
        Proxy->>Registry: HTTP Request (localhost)<br/>8080/TCP<br/>No encryption
        Registry->>DB: Query metadata<br/>5432/TCP<br/>Password/cert auth
        DB-->>Registry: Model metadata
        Registry-->>Proxy: JSON Response
        Proxy-->>Service: HTTPS Response
        Service-->>Router: HTTPS Response
        Router-->>Client: JSON Response<br/>TLS 1.3
    else Unauthorized
        Proxy-->>Client: 403 Forbidden
    end

    Note over Client,DB: Flow 2: Operator Reconciliation

    participant Controller as controller-manager
    participant Webhook as Webhook Service<br/>9443/TCP HTTPS

    User->>K8sAPI: kubectl apply ModelRegistry CR
    K8sAPI->>Webhook: POST /validate-modelregistry-*<br/>mTLS<br/>9443/TCP
    Webhook-->>K8sAPI: Validation result
    K8sAPI->>Controller: Watch event<br/>TLS 1.2+
    Controller->>K8sAPI: Create Deployment, Service, Route<br/>TLS 1.2+<br/>ServiceAccount token
    K8sAPI-->>Controller: Resources created
    Controller->>K8sAPI: Update CR status<br/>TLS 1.2+

    Note over Client,DB: Flow 3: Internal Model Registry Access (No Proxy)

    participant InternalPod as Internal Pod

    InternalPod->>Service: GET /api/model_registry/v1alpha3/models<br/>8080/TCP HTTP<br/>No auth
    Service->>Registry: HTTP Request
    Registry->>DB: Query<br/>5432/TCP
    DB-->>Registry: Results
    Registry-->>Service: JSON Response
    Service-->>InternalPod: JSON Response
